members.member:

PrioritizeAccuracy

/// 
    Turns on results during solve

member.remarks:
Each chunk contains a single list of graphs in this format:

{
  "kind": "graphs",
  "items": {
    "the-first-graph":
    {
      "kind": "graph",
      "facts": [
        ["subject", "quality", "value"],
        ...
      ]
    },
    ...
    "the-last-graph":
    {
      "kind": "graph",
      "facts": [
        ["subject", "quality", "value"],
        ...
      ]
    }
  ]
}

members.member:

Returns if an object is selectable based on the selection filters and allowed entity type for the operation

/// DocObject
Whether object is selectable

member.example:
Calling this:
var index = FindIndexByDescriptionPrefix( "txt files (*.txt)|*.txt|All files (*.*)|*.*", "All files")
...would set index to 2.

Calling this:
var index = FindIndexByFilePattern( "txt files (*.txt)|*.txt|All files (*.*)|*.*", "*.*")
...would set index to 2.
